    <!-- FOR SEAFARERS -->
    <section id="for-seafarers" class="section">
      <div class="container two-column">
        <div>
          <h2>For Individual Seafarers</h2>
          <p>
            Whether you are an AB planning to become Officer,  
            or a young Chief Officer preparing for command, coaching can help you:
          </p>
          <ul class="checklist">
            <li>Clarify your next career steps.</li>
            <li>Improve communication with senior officers and management.</li>
            <li>Build confidence during critical operations and inspections.</li>
            <li>Develop habits that support long-term growth, not just the next contract.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="panel">
          <h3>How a coaching program works</h3>
          <ol>
            <li>Short introductory call to understand your goals.</li>
            <li>Agree on a 4–8 session coaching plan.</li>
            <li>Online or onboard sessions, with simple actions between each one.</li>
            <li>Final review and next-step roadmap.</li>
          </ol>
          <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-block">Start with an intro call</a>
        </div>
      </div>
